title: Linguaphone Polish (1992) Pdf's+Audio
description:
Linguaphone's Polish course (1992) with three PDF's and audio files


Target language: Polish
Source language: English


Notes:

1. Three PDF's: Coursebook, Handbook, and Written Exercises.

2. Audio: the audio is complete but not split.

3. This course follows the 1970s format (i.e., each lesson has three parts) but updated to include written exercises. 

4. Thirty lessons.
